          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>The Minority Summer Workshop was a joint effort between the University of Michigan, Michigan State University and Wayne State University. Marzolf was instrumental in seeking funding and support within the university and from grant agencies, particularly the Dow Jones Fund. Correspondence between units, schools and grant agencies reveal the successes as well as the problems of the program. Schedules, reports and proposals provide a picture of the workshop as a whole.</p>
